{"tid":2182834,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[中大JJ]揸車入中大問題","createTime":"2020-08-31T14:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T14:25:31.000Z","uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"971c11dce094877c595365e4772237734e644a02","tid":2182834,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:25:31.000Z","msg":"想問下有無Ching 知道而家揸車入中大係咪就咁拍八達通就OK?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進出校園<br />\n所有進出校園的車輛須具有下列其中一項認可方式：<br />\n(a) 持有由保安處發出的射頻識別卡 (RFID) 及有效大學泊車證；或<br />\n(b) 持有中大通 (已獲發有效大學泊車證)； 或<br />\n(c) 持有八達通 ；<br />\n政府車輛、認可維修車輛，及獲保安處許可的其他車輛可以進出校園。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.scu.cuhk.edu.hk/index.php/zh/2014-03-24-07-40-14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scu.cuhk.edu.hk%2Findex.php%2Fzh%2F2014-03-24-07-40-14&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=54c39600\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.scu.cuhk.edu.hk/index.php/zh/2014-03-24-07-40-14</a>"}]}